"   (For additional information",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?39/60/40899?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Acyclovir (topical): Patient drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   and",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"UTD.htm?8/51/9011?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Acyclovir (topical): Pediatric drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   )",
"   <br/>",
"   For abbreviations and symbols that may be used in Lexicomp (",
